# Roadmap

Phase 1 (MVP):
- CLI + config + allowlist enforcement
- fetcher + 4-6 checks
- JSON + HTML report
- tests for checks

Phase 2 (Product polish):
- scoring rubric + category scores
- baseline comparison (diff vs last scan)
