Phase 3 (Portfolio flex):
- GitHub Action integration (PR comment + failing thresholds)
- “Fix guidance” snippets per framework (Next.js, Nginx, ASP.NET)

Phase 4 (Nice-to-have):
- PDF output
- dashboard viewer for reports
